Entries.default:
"Pfeh! More filthy kithlings?"

The nāga narrows her eyes and lets out a prolonged hiss.
"Deep Hunter goes free if I must slither over your corpse to reach him!"
"There's no need for this to get ugly. I'm a friend of Sugaan."

"I will suck the sweet marrow from your kithling bones!" 

Hissing, the nāga whips its body to close the distance.

"Guardian! Servant of the isles. Magnificent, resplendent..."

The nāga sways in slow, repetitive motions as she delves into recollection. She snaps out of it before you can try anything.

"Huana stole him from us! Must not delay with kithling chatter!"

Letting out a wet cackle, the nāga signals the others to attack.
"What's the hurry? Can't we talk about this?"
[Attack] "Once you're dead you'll realize what a mistake this was."
"Sugaan?" Her eyes twitch left and right.

"Bah! Ignorant one thinks every nāga same tribe?

"Once we have Deep Hunter, nāga will be strongest in the isles again!"
